This is the README file for Uncertainty Quantification using Polynomial Chaos Expansion (UQPCE).

To set up UQPCE for use:

1) Ensure all of the requirements from the documentation are met.
   - Alternatively, create a conda environment using the environment.yml file
	 provided in the UQPCE/env folder. 
2) Add the folder UQPCE/src to the PATH and PYTHONPATH.
3) In a directory containing an input.yaml, run_matrix.dat, and results.dat, run 
   "python -m PCE_Codes".